      "containerId": null, "originalText": "Step 1:  Brainstorm 5 problems your ideal\n         patient/client has\n\nStep 2:  Pick the ONE that's most common & urgent\n\nStep 3:  Choose a format\n         (checklist, guide, quiz, template, etc.)\n\nStep 4:  Draft the outline\n         (use Claude AI to speed this up!)\n\nStep 5:  Design it (Canva or Gamma)", "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.25,
